file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:8080

paths:
  /auth:
    post:
      operationId: postAuth
      tags:
        - TodoList
      summary: Get a bearer token
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
  /item:
    get:
      operationId: getItems
      security:
        - bearerToken: []
      tags:
        - TodoList
      summary: List all items
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Item"
    post:
      operationId: postItem
      security:
        - bearerToken: []
      tags:
        - TodoList
      summary: Create a new todo list item
      requestBody:
        description: New item
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Item"
      responses:
        "201":
          description: Created
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Item"

  /item/{item_id}:
    get:
      operationId: getItem
      security:
        - bearerToken: []
      tags:
        - TodoList
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: item_id
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Item"
    put:
      operationId: putItem
      security:
        - bearerToken: []
      tags:
        - TodoList
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: item_id
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
      requestBody:
        description: Updated item
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Item"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Item"
    delete:
      operationId: deleteItem
      security:
        - bearerToken: []
      tags:
        - TodoList
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: item_id
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Item"

components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerToken:
      type: http
      scheme:
      bearerFormat: jwt
  schemas:
    Item:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        title:
          type: string
        description:
          type: string
        done:
          type: boolean
      required:
        - id
        - title
        - description
        - done
